lass="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-8">יתרונות למרפאה שלך</h2></div><div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12"><div class="space-y-4"><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-dark">הזדמנויות הכנסה חדשות</h3><p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">הצע תוכניות טיפול מבוססות מנוי למצבים כרוניים וקצרי טווח - בניית זרם הכנסה בר קיימא תוך תמיכה בתוצאות טובות יותר למטופלים.</p></div><div class="space-y-4"><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-dark">מעורבות מטופלים חזקה יותר</h3><p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">שמור על חיבור מטופלים דרך הפורטל ואפליקציית הנייד שלהם, עם תזכורות, התראות ונקודות מגע מתמשכות שמשפרות היענות.</p></div><div class="space-y-4"><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-dark">יעילות תפעולית</h3><p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">משולב בצורה חלקה עם פגישות, חיוב, התראות וזרימות עבודה לייעוץ - בלי כניסות נוספות או כלים עצמאיים.</p></div><div class="space-y-4"><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-dark">מוכן לעתיד</h3><p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">נתוני ניטור מטופלים מרחוק מעשירים את סופר הבינה המלאכותית, עוזרים לנותני שירות ליצור תיעוד ותובנות קליניות חכמות יותר.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Customer Success Stories</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->Allowing doctors to offer telemedicine, remote monitoring health plans, collect payments and the health blog are some of the best features of the Virtual Practice®.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Gerard Saltibus MD</p><p class="text-gray-600">General Practitioner, St. Lucia</p></div></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->I have been using the  continuous care platform for several months and it has made a big impact in my practice allowing me to monitor my patients more efficiently.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Marie Christina Felix Douyon</p><p class="text-gray-600">Pulmonologist, Haiti</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is Remote Patient Monitoring (RPM)?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Remote Patient Monitoring (RPM) is a way for healthcare providers to track patient health data (like blood pressure, glucose, weight, or recovery progress) between visits. Using connected health trackers and apps, providers can deliver continuous care while patients stay at home."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How can RPM help my practice generate revenue?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Clinics can offer RPM as a subscription care plan, charging patients monthly or otherwise for ongoing monitoring. For chronic conditions or post-surgical care, these plans create predictable recurring revenue while improving patient outcomes."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What conditions can be monitored with RPM?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Our system supports 70+ health trackers, enabling setup of plans covering chronic diseases like diabetes, hypertension, hypertension, COPD, skin conditions etc. as well as short-term monitoring needs such as post-surgery recovery."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do I need a separate system for RPM?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. Our Remote Monitoring feature is fully integrated with your EHR, appointments, billing, and consultations. This means no extra logins or disconnected workflows — everything stays in your Virtual Practice."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does RPM improve patient engagement?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Patients can log data through their mobile app or connect popular devices like blood pressure monitors and wearables. This keeps them actively involved in their care, while providers receive alerts and can step in before issues escalate."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Remote Patient Monitoring secure and compliant?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. All data is stored in each patient's secure electronic health record, with strict compliance to healthcare privacy and security standards."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does RPM integrate with AI features?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. While RPM itself is provider-driven, patient data from monitoring is automatically added to the EHR. This data is also considered by our AI Scribe feature, helping providers generate richer, more accurate clinical documentation."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How quickly can my practice start offering Remote Monitoring?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"You can set up your first RPM care plan in just a few days. Patients connect their trackers, and providers start receiving real-time data inside the system immediately."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Who monitors the patient data in an RPM care plan?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Each care plan includes a defined monitoring team. Depending on your practice setup, this may include providers at different levels of responsibility. They can monitor and respond to the patients under the plan and also receive alerts when personalized thresholds are crossed (if any set)."}}]}</script><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-